## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="efe39-104">托管实体的生存期未绑定到表示该实体的 .NET 对象的生存期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efe39-104">The lifetime of a managed entity is not bound to the lifetime of the .NET object representing it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="efe39-105">提供程序可以使用用此特性标记的方法创建相应托管实体的新实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efe39-105">The provider can use the method marked with this attribute to create a new instance of the corresponding managed entity.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="efe39-106">方法参数应该与类绑定构造函数的参数具有相同的名称和类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efe39-106">The method parameters should have the same name and type as the parameters of the class binding constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="efe39-107">使用此属性不会对存储库中的 WMI 类的注册产生任何影响。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efe39-107">Use of this attribute does not have any affect on registration of the WMI class in the repository.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="efe39-108">它仅在运行时使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efe39-108">It is only used at runtime.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="efe39-109">下面的示例演示如何使用 ManagementCreate 特性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efe39-109">The following example demonstrates how to use the ManagementCreate attribute.</span></span>  
  
```  
[ManagementEntity]  
public class ProcessInstance  
{  
     [ManagementKey]  
     public int Id;   
  
     [ManagementCreate]  
     public ProcessInstance StartProcess(string cmdLine)  
     {  
        ProcessInstance newProcess = new ProcessInstance(cmdLine);  
        newProcess.Start();  
        return newProcess;  
     }  
}  
```
